    {
      "href": "/saithkar/list/hyperlink-cinema/",
      "user": "saithkar",
      "slug": "hyperlink-cinema",
      "title": "Hyperlink cinema",
      "desc": "Films that tell multiple (at least three) seemingly unconnected stories that eventually merge or run across one another. \"Normal\" cinematic storytelling usually has either a single main character who we follow and/or an A and a B plot that run in parallel – \"meanwhile back at the ranch\". Hyperlink cinema is a way to to tell otherwise distinctive and fragmented stories that are united by either characters, location or a theme, sometimes all three.",
      "owner": "List by Nick Langdon PATRON",
      "tags": []
    },
    {
