      "title": "Hyperlink Cinema",
      "desc": "According to Wikipedia, “Hyperlink cinema is a style of filmmaking characterised by complex or multilinear narrative structures, which are used in ways that are informed by the World Wide Web.”",
      "owner": "List by Lubby T. PRO",
